title: Babylone - Zina
description:
Babylone is an Algerian band formed in 2012, they tries to introduce their music in different sounds from different musical styles such as Country / Blues / Flamenco / Folk and various other styles ...
Here is their first song called (Zina) it may refer to a beautiful girl or to a name,
I hope you will like it. Please like, share and subscribe for more videos
For more information about the band visit :
